<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subjects - Gumi Smart Learning</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/responsive.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Language Toggle -->
    <div class="language-toggle">
        <button class="lang-btn active" data-lang="en">English</button>
        <button class="lang-btn" data-lang="ko">한국어</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="logo">
                <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
                <span class="lang-en">Gumi Smart Learning</span>
                <span class="lang-ko" style="display:none;">구미 스마트 학습</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="nav-menu">
                <li><a href="index.html" class="nav-link lang-en">Home</a><a href="index.html" class="nav-link lang-ko" style="display:none;">홈</a></li>
                <li><a href="subjects.html" class="nav-link active lang-en">Subjects</a><a href="subjects.html" class="nav-link active lang-ko" style="display:none;">과목</a></li>
                <li><a href="ai-course.html" class="nav-link lang-en">AI Course</a><a href="ai-course.html" class="nav-link lang-ko" style="display:none;">AI 코스</a></li>
                <li><a href="dashboard.html" class="nav-link lang-en">Dashboard</a><a href="dashboard.html" class="nav-link lang-ko" style="display:none;">대시보드</a></li>
                <li><a href="profile.html" class="nav-link lang-en">Profile</a><a href="profile.html" class="nav-link lang-ko" style="display:none;">프로필</a></li>
                <li><button onclick="logout()" class="btn btn-outline lang-en">Logout</button><button onclick="logout()" class="btn btn-outline lang-ko" style="display:none;">로그아웃</button></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="hamburger">
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="dashboard-header">
                <div class="welcome-message">
                    <h1 class="lang-en">Learning Subjects</h1>
                    <h1 class="lang-ko" style="display:none;">학습 과목</h1>
                    <p class="lang-en">Choose your subject and difficulty level to start learning</p>
                    <p class="lang-ko" style="display:none;">과목과 난이도를 선택하여 학습을 시작하세요</p>
                </div>
                <a href="dashboard.html" class="btn btn-outline lang-en">Back to Dashboard</a>
                <a href="dashboard.html" class="btn btn-outline lang-ko" style="display:none;">대시보드로 돌아가기</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="subjects-grid" id="subjectsContainer">
                <!-- Subjects will be loaded by JavaScript -->
            </div>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 60px; text-align: center;">
                <h2 class="section-title lang-en">How to Use the Subjects</h2>
                <h2 class="section-title lang-ko" style="display:none;">과목 사용 방법</h2>
                <div class="features-grid">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-mouse-pointer"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="lang-en">1. Select Subject</h3>
                        <h3 class="lang-ko" style="display:none;">1. 과목 선택</h3>
                        <p class="lang-en">Choose from six major subjects</p>
                        <p class="lang-ko" style="display:none;">6대 주요 과목 중 선택하세요</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-signal"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="lang-en">2. Choose Difficulty</h3>
                        <h3 class="lang-ko" style="display:none;">2. 난이도 선택</h3>
                        <p class="lang-en">Select High, Medium, or Low difficulty</p>
                        <p class="lang-ko" style="display:none;">고급, 중급, 초급 난이도 중 선택하세요</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="lang-en">3. Start Learning</h3>
                        <h3 class="lang-ko" style="display:none;">3. 학습 시작</h3>
                        <p class="lang-en">AI assistant will guide you through lessons</p>
                        <p class="lang-ko" style="display:none;">AI 도우미가 수업을 안내해 드립니다</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- AI Chatbot Widget -->
    <div class="chatbot-widget">
        <div class="chatbot-header">
            <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
            <span class="lang-en">AI Learning Assistant</span>
            <span class="lang-ko" style="display:none;">AI 학습 도우미</span>
            <button class="close-chatbot"><i class="fas fa-times"></i></button>
        </div>
        <div class="chatbot-body">
            <div class="chat-messages">
                <div class="message ai">
                    <div class="message-content lang-en">
                        I can help you with any subject! Which one would you like to learn?
                    </div>
                    <div class="message-content lang-ko" style="display:none;">
                        어떤 과목이든 도와드릴 수 있습니다! 어떤 과목을 배우고 싶으신가요?
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="chat-input">
                <input type="text" id="chatInput" placeholder="Type your question...">
                <button id="sendChat"><i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i></button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="chatbot-toggle">
            <i class="fas fa-comment-dots"></i>
        </button>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-logo">
                    <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
                    <span class="lang-en">Gumi Smart Learning</span>
                    <span class="lang-ko" style="display:none;">구미 스마트 학습</span>
                </div>
                <p class="footer-text lang-en">AI-powered smart learning platform for students in Gumi City</p>
                <p class="footer-text lang-ko" style="display:none;">구미시 학생들을 위한 AI 기반 스마트 학습 플랫폼</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p class="lang-en">&copy; 2024 Gumi Smart Learning Support Service. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p class="lang-ko" style="display:none;">&copy; 2024 구미 스마트 학습 지원 서비스. 모든 권리 보유.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="js/main.js"></script>
    <script src="js/language.js"></script>
    <script src="js/auth.js"></script>
    <script src="js/chatbot.js"></script>
</body>
</html>